songs.title: Temprano
songs.lyrics:
[Instrumental Intro]

[Verse 1: Javier Arce]
Temprano va, asume
Lo que sienten los demás
Tirando piedras al aire
Creyéndose el rey del lugar

[Pre-Chorus: Javier Arce]
Y yo que te quiero liberar
Huyamos rápido de este lugar

[Chorus: Javier Arce]
Runaway with me
Stop your fighting and struggling
Runaway with me
Stop your fighting and struggling
Runaway with me
Stop your fighting and struggling
Runaway with me
Stop your fighting and struggling

[Verse 2: Andrew Tosh]
I man want to take yuh to a place far away
Where is only love and happiness everyday
Fi protect you i will be there
Come baby dont badda fried to come ova here

[Verse 3: Andrew Tosh]
I say dry your tears
Stop lying to yourself and step to another stage
This race, anytime and any place
Yuh can win it even if yuh dont reach in first place

[Verse 4: Javier Arce]
Y quien le cree
Hablando solamente
De lo que ve
Tirando veneno al aire
Creyéndose el cacique del lugar

[Chorus: Javier Arce]
Runaway with me
Stop your fighting and struggling
Runaway with me
Stop your fighting and struggling

[Outro]
Runaway
Runaway
Runaway
